Package: mmcsd
Title: A package to deal with complex longitudinal survey data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Pedro",
           family = "Pacheco",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "pedrohmp36@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4804-1576"))
Description: A package to deal with complex longitudinal survey data. It combines
    longitudinal methodology models with complex sampling design. It fits fixed
    and random effects models and covariance structured models so far. It also
    provides tools to perform statistical tests considering these specifications.
License: GPL (>= 3)
